ZH: 我们要赶快搭上末班车去市中心。
EN: We need to catch the last bus to the city center.
ZH: 我们走得太慢，没有搭上火车。
EN: We walked too slowly and missed the train.
ZH: 昨天我差点搭上错车。 
EN: I almost took the wrong train yesterday.
ZH: 他们在街角搭上了一辆出租车。
EN: They hailed a taxi at the street corner.
ZH: 我们必须搭上这班飞机，没有其他选择了。
EN: We have to catch this flight, there is no other option.
ZH: 饭没吃饱就搭上公共汽车了。
EN: They boarded the bus without finishing their meal.
ZH: 你们能不能快点，我们要搭上火车。
EN: Can you hurry up, we need to catch the train.
ZH: 明天我们准时搭上一起去看电影。
EN: Tomorrow we will all catch a movie together on time.
ZH: 我可以帮你搭上出租车到机场。
EN: I can help you get a taxi to the airport.
ZH: 他因为睡过头，差点搭上相亲的约会。
EN: He almost missed his blind date because he slept in.
ZH: 我们提前搭上电梯直接到了顶楼。
EN: We took the elevator and went straight to the top floor.
ZH: 他们搭上了朋友的车一起去购物中心。
EN: They caught a ride with their friend to the shopping mall.
ZH: 半路上我们搭上了一辆公共汽车。
EN: We caught a bus halfway through the journey.
ZH: 他们未能搭上最后一班渡轮到达岛屿。
EN: They failed to catch the last ferry to the island.
ZH: 我们在机场赶紧搭上了停靠的班车。
EN: We quickly caught the shuttle bus at the airport.
ZH: 他们在街边搭上了一个出租车到达目的地。
EN: They hailed a taxi on the street to reach their destination.
ZH: 我们得争分夺秒，否则要搭上迟到的名单了。
EN: We need to hurry up, or we will end up on the latecomers list.
ZH: 每天晨练后，我总是搭上公车去上班。
